org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.StateBased.StateBasedAnalysis

Interface StateBasedAnalysis

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.CoreElements.Configuration, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Annexes.VSL.Variables.ExpressionContext, org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.GQAM.GaAnalysisContext, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StateBasedAnalysisImpl

    public interface StateBasedAnalysis
extends org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.GQAM.GaAnalysisContext
    A representation of the model object 'State Based Analysis'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Measure
    • Measure Evaluation Result
    • Eval Method
    • Target Failure Mode
    • Target Dep Component
    • Target Port
    • Initial Conditions
    See Also:
    StateBasedAnalysisPackage.getStateBasedAnalysis()
